
{center}
{subhead} Settlers 2{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

It has been confirmed that Titan Computers ( {bold}http://www.titancomputer.de/{nobold} )
are to produce an Amiga port of Settlers 2, the sequel to the hit Amiga game
which has up until now been available only for the PC.
{p} {p}
Specifications for the game are believed to include network play, and you're
looking at needing 16MB RAM, 40MB disk space, and a '030 to play the game.
Further details when we get them!